                             'Lightnix' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Lightnix' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on an 8 by 8 tiles board,
where you click on tiles of various shapes, this will send
'lightning bolts' in 4 directions, vertically and horizontally.
If lightning bolts hit identical tiles, those tiles will be
eliminated and you will get points according to the number of
removed tiles.

  Have fun!

